ACADEMIC CITATION REQUIREMENT
==============================
If you use Vibe Science in research that leads to a publication, presentation,
or any public scientific output, you are required to cite:

  Russo, C. & Bertelli, E. (MD) (2026). Vibe Science: an AI-native research
  engine with adversarial review and serendipity tracking.
  https://github.com/th3vib3coder/vibe-science

See CITATION.cff for machine-readable citation metadata.

